    "effect": {
      "before": "",
      "after": "<p>This ability gains an edge against demons, devils, undead, and creatures not native to your current world. If you know the target’s true name, this ability has a double edge. While [[/apply ztBgmMZaY9rbNmZD]], the target is sent to another manifold in the timescape and removed from the encounter map. A banished target can do nothing but make saving throws, and takes [[/damage 10 holy]] damage each time they do so. If the target is reduced to 0 Stamina while banished, they are lost to the timescape.</p>"
